    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface Functions.CheckedFunction<T,R>
extends Functions.CheckedFunction1<T,R>
    Checked version of java.util.function.Function. Essentially the same as CheckedFunction1<T, R>, or short X1<T, R>.
